Package gameobjects

Class GameObject

java.lang.Object
gameobjects.GameObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Bloon, Button, Projectile, Tower
public abstract class GameObject extends Object
An abstract class defining a game object - an object that exists and interacts with other game objects inside of a game scene.
